{"tid":492124,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[戒賭] 分析騰訊 700  -「食重貨區」講法根本無用 (3)","createTime":"2017-12-07T08:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T07:42:42.000Z","uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6aea6ecfd6678ae1ccaa716a901bb57d5962be","tid":492124,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"又係我。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚哈姆太郎果然發功！今日掂番上通道底。<br />\n<br />\n外圍︰明顯呢幾日股價走勢同納指好大關係。繼續留意納指！<br />\n<br />\n「食重貨區」ga講法根本無用，重貨區日日都有，唔通日日都跌？勸你地唔好信十足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/161500_1cf127559c95a3af29d42e096dbd44ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F161500_1cf127559c95a3af29d42e096dbd44ab.png&h=b4f1e791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一個PO︰[戒賭] 分析騰訊 700 討論 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/491344/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/491344/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a2268a296d5813c9ce6ad8724b9b99814f25092","tid":492124,"uid":13420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:21:31.000Z","msg":"亂嗡廿四"},{"pid":"ef31d25b622542732cc127a51b6663644164783b","tid":492124,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"技術位置可參考番上一個PO<br />\n<br />\n上一個PO︰[戒賭] 分析騰訊 700 討論 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/491344/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/491344/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/quote]"},{"pid":"3d13bc602177f1572a858ea31b4e05e14d624d9a","tid":492124,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:23:45.000Z","msg":"「食重貨區」ga講法根本無用，重貨區日日都有，唔通日日都跌？勸你地唔好信十足。&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;係, 咩叫重貨區, 有幾重, 睇過, 有無$439個陣時咁重先"},{"pid":"d7281d8bc4d97c07f0ff3095afde6e5b2afd3dfd","tid":492124,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「食重貨區」ga講法根本無用，重貨區日日都有，唔通日日都跌？勸你地唔好信十足。&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;係, 咩叫重貨區, 有幾重, 睇過, 有無$439個陣時咁重先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢D數太易睇。如果統計上相關性大一定有人大做文章。<br />\n<br />\n另外，同開賭場一樣，莊家根本實賺，但唔係一定要犯規先有賺，而係一早計好曬點玩都賺。當然可以洗橫手。<br />\n<br />\n但莊家之間都可以互相博弈，食舊錢分分鐘更多。呢D散戶根本無可能計到。不如唔好曬時間。"},{"pid":"b3f9201642b34de8b80e5aa47a90d9302a35ada1","tid":492124,"uid":58049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"會否升到通道頂？"},{"pid":"ce2e8039690d2fcfa62ca4568dd2b15bed2e5e2e","tid":492124,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b6f4ac6d46952f96d591239b69df1cf0ee2c82","tid":492124,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得兩日唔會叫做企穩。"},{"pid":"605d897007592ad4913800f553de308b34024b17","tid":492124,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會否升到通道頂？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n短期內難D。望佢守番入通道內先。<br />\n<br />\n都係個句：留意納指"},{"pid":"d7625e7da54132bb19abc5a7f0b70259e66d6520","tid":492124,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"成功入番通道。納指好野!"},{"pid":"ae8a571b7f4c496020637c8084db7d921c996739","tid":492124,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"開左幾隻700 bear, 輸70%ing 可以點做，sh?"},{"pid":"30e85a326b533284454743cf750c79e30d848239","tid":492124,"uid":72304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開左幾隻700 bear, 輸70%ing 可以點做，sh?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nStrong hold please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4a91c467f5006d037d2ca440a4db0322dc970d","tid":492124,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開左幾隻700 bear, 輸70%ing 可以點做，sh?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nStrong hold please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n升完未？"},{"pid":"55e590d84bd737ca8c77c840d40302863d365564","tid":492124,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開左幾隻700 bear, 輸70%ing 可以點做，sh?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nStrong hold please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n升完未？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔 set 止蝕。<br />\n本身係咪預左舊錢可以輸曬? <br />\n<br />\n以家你同賭大細一樣。星期一GA市太難估到。戒賭啦，方法：極細注玩，當食美沙銅。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為牛熊最盡玩法：即日鮮。開市前睇曬d因素，估大方向。開市個位睇反映曬預期升跌。反映曬就忍手。未先可以一搏。但一樣要諗止蝕。<br />\n<br />\n祝你好運ching。我幫你唔到。話知個D你都唔好信。"},{"pid":"134b8ade04094947f61403d46e29d6b279daee71","tid":492124,"uid":42420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:42:42.000Z","msg":"已入通道 是否穩陣？"}]}